    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius</persName> gratia Dei <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si sanctis ac venerabilibus locis
                        munificentiam quamlibet tribuimus largitatis, presentis eterneque vite
                        remunerationem adipisci non titubamus. Idcirco omnium sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        fidelium nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum comperiat solertia, qualiter
                            <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/1500">Beatus</persName> sancte
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/239" key="#Mother_churches"><placeName
                                ref="#places/627">Terdonensis</placeName> ecclesie</orgName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> per <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Bishops" ref="#people/369">Ioannem <placeName
                                ref="#places/65"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/220"
                                    >Ticinensem</orgName></placeName></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Bishops" ref="#people/231">Liutardum <placeName
                                ref="#places/356"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/227"
                                    >Cumanum</orgName></placeName></persName> venerabiles <rs
                            key="#Bishops">presules</rs> nostre sugessit maiestati, ut <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">teloneum</rs> et <rs key="#Profits_of_justice"
                            >districtum</rs> et omnem publicam functionem, sicut hactenus investita
                            <rs key="#Plebs">plebs</rs> de <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Mills #Aqueducts #Plebs #Profits_of_justice #Teloneum #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/241"><placeName ref="#places/621"
                                >Viqueria</placeName></orgName> fuerat, confirmaremus et
                        corroboraremus. Insuper etiam <rs key="#Aqueducts">aqueductum de <rs
                                key="#Rivers">Stafulla</rs></rs> ad <rs key="#Mills">molendina</rs>
                        construenda ad opus eiusdem plebis per quamcunque <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property">terram que nostre pertineret
                            regie potestati</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity">ut nullus in
                            eodem aqueductu sine sua suorumque successorum licentia molendinum
                            construere audeat</rs>, concedere ac donare dignaremur. Quorum
                        petitionibus assensum prebentes, eidem plebi in honorem sancti Laurentii
                        constructe teloneum, districtum et omnem publicam functionem, sicut hactenus
                        tenuit et investita fuit, per hoc nostrum preceptum confirmamus et
                        corroboramus. Insuper etiam largimur et concedimus, ut aqueductum de
                        Stafulla ad molendina conficienda ad opus predicte ecclesie sive per nostram
                        regiam terram sive per <rs key="#Roads">publicam viam</rs> deducat, et si
                        aliqua regia terra ibi vicina est ubi molendinum possit construi ad opus
                        ipsius ecclesie, quantum necesse est ex eadem accipiat terra, et publicam,
                        si opus est, viam incidat. Statuimus quoque et interdicimus, ut <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity">nemo in eodem
                            aqueductu, quem prefatus episcopus vel sui successores fecerint,
                            conficiendi molendinum potestatem habeat nisi consensu et licentia
                            episcopi</rs> qui pro tempore in eadem Terdonensi ecclesia fuerit. Si
                        quis igitur huius precepti violator extiterit, <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            optimi manchosos mille</rs> componere cogatur, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem camere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem rectoribus ipsius
                            ecclesie</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus
                        observetur, manu propria roborantes anuli nostri impressione subter
                        insigniri iussimus. Signum serenissimi (M) Berengarii regis. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216"
                            >Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et [subscripsi]. Data kalendis
                        februarii, [anno] dominice incarnationis DCCCCXVIIII regni domni Berengarii
                        piissimi regis XXVIIII, indictione VIII, Actum in <placeName
                            ref="#places/3600"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential"
                            >Coriano</placeName>, feliciter.</ab>
